Functional Requirements

F1. The system shall be able to recieve route requests.

F2. The system shall be able to calculate time to destination.

F3. The system shall be able to visualize user travel patterns.

F4. The system shall be able to identify blindspots through visualization. 

F5. The system shall be able to receive map coordinates

F6. The system shall be able to receive time stamps

F7. The system shall be able to visualise coordinates on a map


Quality requirements

Q1. The Visualisation should be aesthetically pleasing for the user

Q2. The Visualizer should display data efficiently and fast within a 2 second interval

Q3. The system should be easy to navigate and use


Constraints

C1. System shall follow regulations regarding GDPR

C2. System shall be constriant to work in the Gothenburg area
